            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6117388-malinda?shelf=50-books-in-2019">50-books-in-2019</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6117388-malinda?shelf=24-others-in-2020">24-others-in-2020</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2744305538" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer919320588716076598">Once again, I turned to an old friend. A comfort in crazy times.</span>

          </span>
