        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer138737636" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6301111420057666517">I&apos;ve read all the Dick Francis books over the years, starting back in the 80&apos;s when I found my first tattered copy in a used bookstore. When Dick passed away last year, I decided it was time to rediscover the pleasure of his stories. I particularly enjoyed this story of family dysfunction and greed. I loved the voice of the protagonist and found the mystery to be satisfying. </span>
  <span id="freeText6301111420057666517" style="display:none">I've read all the Dick Francis books over the years, starting back in the 80's when I found my first tattered copy in a used bookstore. When Dick passed away last year, I decided it was time to rediscover the pleasure of his stories. I particularly enjoyed this story of family dysfunction and greed. I loved the voice of the protagonist and found the mystery to be satisfying. </span>
