  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/634007128" />
    <a title="Joanna" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/375767-joanna"><img alt="Joanna" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1189771278p2/375767.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/634007128?book_show_action=true">Jun 05, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Joanna" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Joanna" href="/user/show/375767-joanna">Joanna</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/375767-joanna?shelf=mystery-series-and-not">mystery-series-and-not</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer634007128" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15789827952052709291">This was exactly what I wanted it to be. A Dick Francis &quot;summer read&quot; with a big cast of characters, twisty enough plot, some horse-racing/jockeying, and no actual anxiety. The writing stays on the surface, so I don&apos;t feel too personally invested. Soapy fun!</span>
  <span id="freeText15789827952052709291" style="display:none">This was exactly what I wanted it to be. A Dick Francis "summer read" with a big cast of characters, twisty enough plot, some horse-racing/jockeying, and no actual anxiety. The writing stays on the surface, so I don't feel too personally invested. Soapy fun!</span>
