    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer92602277" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14649794890507744788">One of my favorites books from the nearly always enjoyable Francis. The book is a tangle of greedy heirs, family squabbling, and attempted murder, all done with verve and great characterization.</span>

          </span>
